data.description: Welcome to 21237 Carlysle St., a stylish and well-maintained 3-bed, 1.5-bath bungalow in the heart of Dearborn, MI. Boasting 1,093 sq ft, this home features a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a new furnace (2022), and a convenient 2-car garage. Enjoy comfort and convenience in a prime location with nearby amenities and easy access to major routes. Don't miss the chance to call this charming property your home!
